{"title":"Kanban Board Field Reference","groups":[{"heading":"Job Card Fields","items":[{"label":"Left Border Color","value":"Shows the job's priority at a glance: gray for Low, teal for Normal, orange for High, red for Urgent. It's on every card."},{"label":"Job Number","value":"The job's ID (like JOB-0001), filled in for you. Click it to open the job's full details. Sits at the top of the card."},{"label":"Title","value":"The job's title, shown below the number. If it's too long for the card, the end is trimmed with a '...'."},{"label":"Cover Photo","value":"An optional picture across the top of the card. Set it from the job's details using the cover-photo button."},{"label":"Hold Indicator","value":"A pause icon at the top of the card. It means the job is on hold. Point at it to see why."},{"label":"Overdue Warning","value":"A yellow warning icon at the top of the card. It means the due date has passed and the job isn't finished yet."},{"label":"Assignee","value":"Their initials, shown at the bottom of the card. Hidden when no one is assigned."},{"label":"Customer Name","value":"The customer for this job, shown at the bottom of the card. Hidden when there's no customer."},{"label":"Billing Status Icon","value":"A dollar icon at the bottom of the card. A green check means invoiced; an orange icon means not yet invoiced. Shown only when there's a billing status."},{"label":"Accounting Reference","value":"A receipt icon and number at the bottom of the card, showing the matching document in your accounting system (such as a QuickBooks invoice number). Shown only when the job is linked to accounting."},{"label":"Disposition Icon","value":"A check icon at the bottom of the card. It means the job's output has been dealt with — shipped, stocked, scrapped, and so on."},{"label":"Sub-Jobs Count","value":"A tree icon and number at the bottom of the card, showing how many smaller jobs sit under this one. Shown only when there are some."},{"label":"Due Date","value":"The due date at the bottom of the card. It turns red when the job is overdue, and is hidden when no due date is set."},{"label":"Selected State","value":"When you Ctrl+click a card to select it, it gets a blue check and a highlighted border."}]},{"heading":"Create Job Fields","items":[{"label":"Title (required)","value":"The job's name. Required, up to 200 characters. Can't be left blank."},{"label":"Description","value":"Optional. Any notes about the job's scope, requirements, or details."},{"label":"Track Type (required, when creating)","value":"Pick which workflow the job belongs to: Production, R&D/Tooling, Maintenance, Other, or your own. The job starts in that workflow's first stage. You can't change it later, so it's not shown when editing."},{"label":"Customer","value":"Pick the customer for this job. Optional — choose '-- None --' to leave it out."},{"label":"Assignee","value":"Pick who the job is assigned to. Optional — choose '-- Unassigned --' to leave it open. Anyone who hasn't finished setting up their profile shows a warning icon and '(incomplete profile)'."},{"label":"Priority","value":"Choose Low, Normal (the default), High, or Urgent. This sets the color of the card's left edge on the board."},{"label":"Due Date","value":"Optional. When set, the date shows at the bottom of the card, and the card flags as overdue once the date passes."},{"label":"Save Button","value":"Grayed out until the form is complete, and while it's saving. Point at it to see anything still missing."},{"label":"Draft Auto-Save","value":"The form saves what you type as you go. If you close it by accident, your entries come back the next time you open it."}]},{"heading":"Job Details — Header","items":[{"label":"Job Number","value":"Shown in bold in the top-left corner. You can't edit it."},{"label":"Stage Label","value":"A colored label next to the job number showing the stage the job is in. Its color matches the stage."},{"label":"Start Timer Button","value":"A play icon. Starts tracking time on this job."},{"label":"Stop Timer Button","value":"A stop icon, shown while a timer is running. Stops the timer."},{"label":"Cover Photo Button","value":"A camera icon. Opens a window to set or change the card's cover photo."},{"label":"Edit Button","value":"A pencil icon. Opens the edit form, already filled in with the job's current details."},{"label":"Close Button","value":"An X icon. Closes the details and returns you to the board."}]},{"heading":"Job Details — Main Sections","items":[{"label":"Title & Description","value":"The top of the panel shows the job's title with its description below. If there's no description, it reads 'No description'."},{"label":"R&D Iteration Badge","value":"Shown for R&D/Tooling jobs. Displays which version this is (like v3), plus any iteration notes."},{"label":"Disposition Info","value":"Shown once the job's output has been dealt with. Lists what was done with it (Ship to Customer, Add to Inventory, Capitalize as Asset, Scrap, or Hold for Review), any notes, and the date."},{"label":"Subtasks","value":"A checklist for the job, with a done count (like 3/5). Check an item to mark it done — its text gets crossed out. Type in the box at the bottom and press Enter to add a new one."},{"label":"Sub-Jobs","value":"Smaller jobs that sit under this one. Each shows its number, title, and current stage. Shown only when there are some."},{"label":"Explode BOM Button","value":"Shown when the job is tied to a part and has no sub-jobs yet. Creates a sub-job for each part you make in-house from that part's parts list. Bought parts show up as purchasing suggestions instead, and stocked parts are reserved from inventory."},{"label":"Linked Jobs","value":"Other jobs related to this one. Each shows how they're connected (Related to, Blocks, or Parent of), the job's number, title, and stage, plus a button to remove the link. Search to add a new link and pick how they relate."},{"label":"Parts","value":"Parts attached to this job. Each shows the part number, description, quantity, and a button to remove it. Search to add a part."},{"label":"Cost Analysis","value":"A cost summary showing estimated material, labor, overhead, and subcontract costs, along with the quoted price and the resulting margin."},{"label":"Operation Time","value":"A breakdown of how much time each step of the job takes."},{"label":"Activity / Comments / Notes / History","value":"A running timeline of everything that's happened to the job — changes, comments, notes, and system events. You can comment right here and tag people with @."}]},{"heading":"Job Details — Sidebar","items":[{"label":"Status Timeline","value":"Shows how the job has moved through its stages, with dates and any holds along the way."},{"label":"Dispose Button","value":"Opens a window to record what happens to the job's output. Shown until the job has been disposed. Choices: Ship to Customer, Add to Inventory, Capitalize as Asset, Scrap, or Hold for Review."},{"label":"Barcode / QR Info","value":"Shows the job's barcode so you can scan it."},{"label":"Priority","value":"Shows the job's priority in color: gray for Low, teal for Normal, orange for High, red for Urgent."},{"label":"Assignee","value":"Shows who the job is assigned to. Click it to pick someone else or unassign it. The change saves right away — no need to open the edit form."},{"label":"Customer","value":"The customer for this job. Click it to open the customer's page. Shows '—' when there's no customer."},{"label":"Due Date","value":"When the job is due. Shows nothing when no due date is set."},{"label":"Start Date","value":"When the job started. Set automatically the first time you move it out of its opening stage."},{"label":"Track Type","value":"Which workflow the job belongs to (Production, R&D/Tooling, and so on). Can't be changed."},{"label":"Part","value":"Shown when the job is tied to a part. Click the part number to open the part."},{"label":"Parent Job","value":"Shown when this job sits under a larger one. Click the parent's number to open it."},{"label":"Files","value":"Drag files here to attach them, or click to browse — any file type works. Each attached file has buttons to download or remove it."},{"label":"Time","value":"All the time logged on this job. Each entry shows who, when, how long, and any notes, with the total at the top."}]},{"heading":"Dispose Job Fields","items":[{"label":"Disposition (required)","value":"Pick what happens to the job's output: Ship to Customer, Add to Inventory, Capitalize as Asset, Scrap, or Hold for Review."},{"label":"Notes","value":"Optional. Any extra context for the decision, up to 2000 characters."},{"label":"Dispose Button","value":"Saves the choice and marks the job as disposed. Grayed out until you pick a disposition."}]},{"heading":"Job Statuses (Stage Flow)","items":[{"label":"Quote Requested","value":"The opening stage for Production jobs. The job has been requested but not yet quoted."},{"label":"Quoted (Estimate)","value":"An estimate has been prepared. May create a document in your accounting system if one is connected."},{"label":"Order Confirmed (Sales Order)","value":"The customer accepted the quote, so a sales order is created."},{"label":"Materials Ordered (PO)","value":"Purchase orders have gone out for the materials needed."},{"label":"Materials Received","value":"All the ordered materials have arrived and are ready for production."},{"label":"In Production","value":"The job is being worked on."},{"label":"QC/Review","value":"The job is being inspected and reviewed for quality."},{"label":"Shipped (Invoice)","value":"The job's output has shipped. May create an invoice. Often a one-way stage you can't move back out of."},{"label":"Invoiced/Sent","value":"The invoice has been sent to the customer."},{"label":"Payment Received (Payment)","value":"The final stage. The customer has paid, and the job is marked complete."}]},{"heading":"Priority Levels","items":[{"label":"Low (gray)","value":"Work that isn't urgent. The card's left edge is gray. Sorts to the bottom."},{"label":"Normal (teal)","value":"The default for every new job. The card's left edge is teal."},{"label":"High (orange)","value":"Important work to get to soon. The card's left edge is orange."},{"label":"Urgent (red)","value":"Critical work that needs attention now. The card's left edge is red. Sorts to the top."}]},{"heading":"Bulk Actions","items":[{"label":"Multi-Select","value":"Hold Ctrl (Cmd on Mac) and click cards to select several jobs at once. Selected cards get a blue check. Click any card without Ctrl to clear the selection."},{"label":"Bulk Move","value":"Move all the selected jobs to one stage. A menu lists the stages for this workflow. A message confirms how many moved."},{"label":"Bulk Assign","value":"Assign all the selected jobs to one person. The menu lists your team plus an 'Unassign' option. A message confirms the count and who."},{"label":"Bulk Set Priority","value":"Set the priority on all the selected jobs — Low, Normal, High, or Urgent. A message confirms the priority and count."},{"label":"Bulk Archive","value":"Archive all the selected jobs. You'll be asked to confirm first. Archived jobs leave the board but aren't gone for good — you can restore them later."},{"label":"Clear Selection","value":"The X on the right of the action bar. Unselects every card."}]},{"heading":"Keyboard and Interaction Shortcuts","items":[{"label":"Ctrl+Click card","value":"Adds or removes a card from your current selection."},{"label":"Enter on card","value":"Opens the job's details for the card you're on."},{"label":"Escape (in details)","value":"Closes the job's details."},{"label":"Enter in subtask box","value":"Adds what you typed to the checklist without clicking the add button."},{"label":"Barcode scan","value":"With a USB barcode scanner on the board, scanning a job number finds that job and opens its details."}]},{"heading":"Column Header Elements","items":[{"label":"Stage Name","value":"The name of the stage, shown in the column header."},{"label":"Job Count","value":"How many jobs are in this column right now. Updates on its own as jobs move."},{"label":"WIP Limit","value":"A suggested cap for the column, shown as '/ N' after the count. Set per stage by an admin. Go over it and the count turns red."},{"label":"Lock Icon","value":"A padlock on one-way stages. Jobs can't be dragged backward out of them. Point at it and it explains: 'Irreversible — jobs cannot move backward from this stage'."},{"label":"Color Stripe","value":"The colored strip across the top of the column, matching the stage's color, so each column is easy to spot."}]},{"heading":"WIP Limits","items":[{"label":"Purpose","value":"A WIP limit is a suggested cap on how many jobs a stage should hold, so it doesn't get overloaded. It's just a guide — you can still add more, but the count turns red to warn you."},{"label":"Setup","value":"An admin sets it per stage under Admin → Track Types → Stages. Enter 0 or leave it blank for no limit."},{"label":"Visual Warning","value":"When a column goes over its limit, the count and the '/ N' next to it turn red. The column's border may change too."},{"label":"How Strict It Is","value":"WIP limits only warn — they never stop you from moving a job. That way you stay flexible for urgent work while still seeing where things pile up."}]},{"heading":"Validation Rules","items":[{"label":"Title (Create/Edit)","value":"Required, and can't be blank. Up to 200 characters. If it's missing, you'll see 'Title is required.'"},{"label":"Track Type (Create)","value":"Required. Pick a workflow — one is chosen for you if a default exists. If it's missing, you'll see 'Track Type is required.'"},{"label":"Backward Move Restriction","value":"You can't move a job backward out of a one-way stage. The card slides back and you'll see 'Cannot move backward from irreversible stage.'"},{"label":"Cross-Track Move","value":"You can't move a job into a stage that belongs to a different workflow — the move is turned away."},{"label":"Assignee Setup","value":"When you assign a job, anyone who hasn't finished setting up their profile shows a warning icon. You can still assign them."},{"label":"Disposition (required)","value":"To dispose a job, you must pick what happens to its output. Notes are optional (up to 2000 characters)."},{"label":"Subtask Text","value":"The add button stays grayed out until you type something in the subtask box."},{"label":"Link Target","value":"The add button stays grayed out until you pick a job to link from the search results."}]},{"heading":"Board and Table Actions","items":[{"label":"Switch Track Type","value":"Click a track type to load that workflow's board. The board reloads for the new one."},{"label":"Switch View","value":"Toggle between Board View (the default columns) and Team View (a grid of jobs by person)."},{"label":"Drag Card Between Columns","value":"Moves the job to that stage. It moves right away, and slides back if the move isn't allowed."},{"label":"Drag Card Within Column","value":"Reorders the card within its stage. Its place is saved for you."},{"label":"Drag Card in Team View","value":"Dragging a card can change both its stage and who it's assigned to at once."},{"label":"Click Job Number","value":"Opens the job's full details. The web address updates so you can copy it to share the job."},{"label":"Click Card","value":"If cards are selected, clears the selection. Otherwise opens the job's details."},{"label":"Edit Job","value":"Opens the edit form, already filled in. Saving updates the board."},{"label":"Quick-Assign","value":"Click the assignee in the job's sidebar and pick someone else. The change saves right away — no edit form needed."},{"label":"Add Subtask","value":"Type in the subtask box and press Enter or click add. It shows up in the checklist right away."},{"label":"Check Off Subtask","value":"Click a subtask's checkbox to mark it done or not — its text crosses out when done."},{"label":"Add Link","value":"Search for a job, pick it from the results, choose how they relate (Related to, Blocks, Parent of), and click add."},{"label":"Remove Link","value":"Click the X on a linked job to remove the link."},{"label":"Add Part","value":"Search for a part, pick it from the results, and click add. It shows up in the parts list with its quantity."},{"label":"Remove Part","value":"Click the X on a part to take it off the job."},{"label":"Explode BOM","value":"Click 'Explode BOM' on a job that's tied to a part. It creates sub-jobs from the part's parts list. Shown only when the job has a part and no sub-jobs yet."},{"label":"Start/Stop Timer","value":"Click the timer button at the top of the job's details to start timing it. Click again to stop. Entries show up in the sidebar's Time section."},{"label":"Upload File","value":"Drag files onto the upload area in the sidebar, or click to browse. You'll see them appear in the file list."},{"label":"Download File","value":"Click the download icon on a file to save it."},{"label":"Delete File","value":"Click the red delete icon on a file to remove it from the job."},{"label":"Dispose Job","value":"Click Dispose in the sidebar. A window opens to pick what happens to the output and add notes. Choices: Ship to Customer, Add to Inventory, Capitalize as Asset, Scrap, or Hold for Review."}]},{"heading":"Link Types","items":[{"label":"Related to","value":"A general connection between two jobs. It shows on both jobs."},{"label":"Blocks","value":"This job is holding up the other one. Use it to track what depends on what."},{"label":"Parent of","value":"This job is the parent of the other one. Use it to group jobs under a larger one."}]}]}
"""
